Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Output gifs/privacy-read-proof.gif

Hide
Type "export PS1='user@bray:bray $ '"
Enter
Type "alias claude=./site/demos/bray-demo.sh"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Type "claude -p 'Describe what privacy-read-proof does for reading published proofs'"
Enter
Sleep 12s
